description:
This torrent contains all episodes from the start untill 2005-05-30 of 8-Bit Theater for easy offline viewing.

8-Bit Theater (also spelled 8-Bit Theatre) is a popular sprite comic created and launched by Brian Clevinger in March 2001 and will end sometime in 2008. It won the Web Cartoonist's Choice Awards for best fantasy comic in 2002. In its feature on gaming webcomics, 1UP.com described 8-Bit Theater as the sprite comic &quot;that took the style to its fullest expression and greatest popularity.&quot;

